{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781723710920,"sessionID":"ses_128ff49bbffeaBi7hiBur0TbQX","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"grep","callID":"tool_rvGeikflCZ64J4kvyD5wrssS","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"reorderTopNByCosine|resolveAbsoluteRelevance|enrichFusedResults|COSINE_TOPN_REORDER_DEPTH","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/hybrid-search.ts"},"output":"Found 19 matches\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/hybrid-search.ts:\n  Line 30: import { resolveAbsoluteRelevance, type PipelineRow } from './pipeline/types.js';\n\n  Line 341: let enrichFusedResultsObserver: (() => void) | null = null;\n\n  Line 1288:     return enrichFusedResults(query, execution, options);\n\n  Line 1676: async function enrichFusedResults(\n\n  Line 1682:   enrichFusedResultsObserver?.();\n\n  Line 2024:       reranked = reorderTopNByCosine(reranked);\n\n  Line 2164:       ? enrichFusedResults(query, finalStage.execution, finalStage.options, finalStage.results)\n\n  Line 2416: const COSINE_TOPN_REORDER_DEPTH = 10;\n\n  Line 2421:  * Reorders only the top-N by absolute cosine relevance (resolveAbsoluteRelevance),\n\n  Line 2429: function reorderTopNByCosine(\n\n  Line 2431:   depth: number = COSINE_TOPN_REORDER_DEPTH\n\n  Line 2440:     .map((row, index) => ({ row, index, relevance: resolveAbsoluteRelevance(row as PipelineRow) }))\n\n  Line 2612:     ? await enrichFusedResults(query, enrichmentExecution, enrichmentOptions, results)\n\n  Line 2915:   reorderTopNByCosine,\n\n  Line 2916:   COSINE_TOPN_REORDER_DEPTH,\n\n  Line 2922:     enrichFusedResultsObserver = observer;\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/confidence-scoring.ts:\n  Line 26: import { resolveEffectiveScore, resolveAbsoluteRelevance, type PipelineRow } from './pipeline/types.js';\n\n  Line 160:     ? resolveAbsoluteRelevance(result as PipelineRow)\n\n\n/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/search/pipeline/types.ts:\n  Line 89: export function resolveAbsoluteRelevance(row: PipelineRow): number {\n","metadata":{"matches":19,"truncated":false},"title":"reorderTopNByCosine|resolveAbsoluteRelevance|enrichFusedResults|COSINE_TOPN_REORDER_DEPTH","time":{"start":1781723710891,"end":1781723710919}},"id":"prt_ed70242f1001uH6fjmkSfzUNIb","sessionID":"ses_128ff49bbffeaBi7hiBur0TbQX","messageID":"msg_ed7022543001TYGfjoNDctOCXT"}}
